<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/home.css">

    <header>
        <img src="/images/DUO.png" alt="Duo avatar">
        <h1>Duo Discord bot</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="description">
            <dt>Introduces voting in your Discord server</dt>
            <dd>Vote by reacting to a message with üëç or üëé</dd>
            <dt>A server member can see their score any time</dt>
            <dd>Ask for your score or the score of others with _score or _lead</dd>
            <dd>
                Scores are saved both server wide and locally for each channel<br>
                so you can see how active people are in the server or in a specific channel
            </dd>
    </div>

    <div class="panel-select">
        <button>Commands</button>
        <button>Future updates</button>
    </div>

    <div class="panels">
        <div id="Commands" class="panel open">
            <h3>Commands</h3>
            <dl>
                <dt>_score</dt>
                <dd>
                    Replies with your score
                    <dl>
                        <dt>Optional: @user mention</dt>
                        <dd>Replies with scores for mentioned users</dd>
                        <dt>Optional: #channel mention</dt>
                        <dd>Replies only with score recieved in the mentioned channel</dd>
                    </dl>
                </dd>
                <dt>_leaderboard</dt>
                    <dd>also: _lead</dd>
                    <dd>
                        Replies with the server's leaderboard
                        <dl>
                            <dt>Optional: #channel mention</dt>
                            <dd>Replies with te channel's leaderboard</dd>
                            <dt>Sorting</dt>
                            <dd>Option: downvotes<br>sorts the leaderboard by downvotes</dd>
                            <dd>Option: upvotes<br>sorts the leaderboard by upvotes</dd>
                        </dl>
                    </dd>
                <dt>_help</dt>
                <dd>Replies with info about bot</dd>
            </dl>
        </div>

        <div id="Future updates" class="panel">
            <h3>Future updates</h3>
            <dl>
                <dt>Emoji</dt>
                <dd>Add the ability to configure, for each guild, whitch emoji are used for voting</dd>
                <dt>Roles</dt>
                <dd>
                    Add more configurability to roles<br>
                    i.e. edit permissions, hoist
                </dd>
                <dd>Add a color picker for easier role editing</dd>
            </dl>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/home.js"></script>
